channel.title: Is this weird?
channel.description: Ok, so last night I had a dream in which I had pulled out my own tooth (lol) and naturally, blood was dripping from my gums. Also, this dream was livid (couldn't control it, but I could feel/taste everything) so I had tasted the blood. When I woke up, I still tasted it, and I still feel like I can a little bit now. So is this a bit weird? Or could I just be thinking about it too much? (I could really be bleeding too, but I doubt it :3)

And I get nose bleeds a lot from my allergies now, and my window was open, so I could have had a mini one somehow o.o oh well, I dont mind the taste of blood at all.
